		""
		"&aProgression works in essence tiers:"
		"&7• &aInferium&r (Tier 1) — the foundation"
		"&7• &ePrudentium&r (Tier 2) — unlocks metals"
		"&7• &6Tertium&r (Tier 3) — diamonds, emeralds"
		"&7• &cImperium&r (Tier 4) — netherite, rare materials"
		"&7• &dSupremium&r (Tier 5) — endgame"
		""
		"Each tier requires 4× of the previous + a central crystal in the &fInfusion Altar&r."
