		"&7• How to start with each mod"
		"&7• How to integrate mods together"
		"&7• Goals to give you direction"
		""
		"&aGood luck. The Legacy Never Dies."
		""
		"&8Pack made by: &7Arena BR O Legado Não Morre"
	]
